{"comments":"Matroid Constraint Types and Instances.\n\nA matroid (V, I) encodes independence constraints:\n- V is the ground set\n- I ⊆ 2^V is the family of independent sets\n\n## Matroid Axioms\n\n1. ∅ ∈ I (empty set is independent)\n2. If A ∈ I and B ⊆ A, then B ∈ I (hereditary)\n3. If A, B ∈ I and |A| < |B|, then ∃e ∈ B\\A : A ∪ {e} ∈ I (exchange)\n\n## Supported Matroids\n\n- **Cardinality**: I = {S ⊆ V : |S| ≤ k}\n- **Partition**: V partitioned into blocks, select ≤ k_i from each\n- **Uniform**: All k-subsets are bases\n- **Graphic**: Independent sets are forests in a graph\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Prelude (Eq, Ord, Show)\n- Hydrogen.Optimize.Submodular.Types.GroundSet\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Tensor.Dimension (Dim)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":"Matroid rank function: r(S) = max{|I| : I ⊆ S, I ∈ I}\n","info":{"declType":"typeClassMember","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"m","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Types","GroundSet"],"ElementSet"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"v","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Types","Matroid"],"MatroidRank"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[121,43],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Optimize/Submodular/Types/Matroid.purs","start":[121,3]},"title":"rank"},{"comments":"Maximum rank (rank of entire ground set)\n","info":{"declType":"typeClassMember","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"conten